Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.93,0:00:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megatron?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.80,0:00:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you've detected the ancient Autobot frequency precisely because it was unearthed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.63,0:00:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,, 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.22,0:00:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, our backup shouldn't be far behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.62,0:00:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without knowing what the Decepticons have exhumed
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.89,0:00:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not think I am willing to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.81,0:00:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.43,0:00:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it to me. With utmost care!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.19,0:01:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megatron!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.87,0:01:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot allow you to pilfer Autobot relics.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.12,0:01:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only are you misinformed, Optimus.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.54,0:01:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I would strongly advise you to lower your weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.59,0:01:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless you're in the mood for mutually assured destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.17,0:01:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.68,0:01:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Spark-Extractor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.72,0:02:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather unassuming...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.82,0:02:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,yet capable of extracting every Spark within its radius.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.99,0:02:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}And to think that you led me straight to it, Optimus!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.43,0:02:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or should I say, Orion Pax did.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.39,0:02:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}You really should have left your Decepticon shield intact.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.44,0:02:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}For you have no idea how useful your code-breaking skills proved to be, during our all too brief time together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.19,0:02:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}Soundwave! Send the Groundbridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.87,0:02:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Engage them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.33,0:03:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bumblebee! Secure the package.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.40,0:03:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.09,0:04:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Loop-de-loop, hah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.57,0:04:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have some brass bearings, Bumblebee.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.03,0:04:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Optimus,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.98,0:04:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.44,0:04:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The source of the ancient frequency we detected.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.53,0:04:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An Iacon homing beacon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.67,0:04:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's an Autobot locator doing on THAT?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.72,0:04:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The class "A" Decepticon weapons confiscated during the War were sealed within the vaults below Iacon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.48,0:04:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where once you worked as an archivist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.93,0:04:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iacon was both a cultural center and a stronghold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.24,0:05:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which Megatron raided when Autobot troops were at their nadir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.41,0:05:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It stands to reason that in anticipation of Iacon being overrun by enemy forces
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.83,0:05:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these weapons were jettisoned off-world to keep them far from Decepticon reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.92,0:05:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clearly, the beacon was added as a safety measure
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.69,0:05:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,should the weapons ever be found by the undesired party.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.05,0:05:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, thanks to our hot-shot stunt driver this one is going in our vault.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.26,0:05:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think this is the only intel you supplied to Megatron?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.12,0:05:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arcee, you are right to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.92,0:05:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I am afraid I... do not remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.16,0:05:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Optimus.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.83,0:05:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megatron clearly took advantage of your amnesia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.96,0:05:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But for all we know this Spark-extractor is the extent of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.59,0:05:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you stopped to consider that he might have suggested otherwise merely to plague your thoughts?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.24,0:05:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Spark-extractor was in my grasp!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.60,0:06:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have removed more than that scout's voice-box
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.43,0:06:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when I had the chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.07,0:06:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, Soundwave.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.33,0:06:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We possess two more sets of coordinates which Orion decrypted before departing our ranks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.17,0:06:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us see what other long lost treasures we might be re-united with.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.05,0:06:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I just picked up the same signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.84,0:06:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could be another homing beacon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.46,0:06:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's rendezvous at the coordinates.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.38,0:07:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silas. Another one's headed to our position.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Estimated arrival - two minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.76,0:07:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Work briskly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.59,0:07:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would appear the signal was a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.87,0:07:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Better Bumblebee than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.86,0:07:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The backup is ahead of schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.63,0:07:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As luck would have it,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.45,0:08:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.02,0:08:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.36,0:08:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bee!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.37,0:08:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who did this? 'Cons?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.08,0:08:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One way to find out. Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.87,0:08:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We rolling’ or not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.23,0:09:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "you can't"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.24,0:09:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can fix Bee, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.23,0:09:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bumblebee was hit pretty hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.91,0:09:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The stun blast may have fried his T-cog.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.69,0:09:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that like a T-bone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.97,0:09:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.21,0:09:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the organ that allows us to scan vehicles and transform.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.09,0:09:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the Allspark!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.31,0:09:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bumblebee's T-cog isn't damaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.78,0:09:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.87,0:09:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Decepticons transform too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.81,0:09:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would they steal that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.16,0:09:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megatron may be known to raise zombies but he is no ghoul.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.84,0:09:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Megatron wasn't behind this then who was?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.23,0:09:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ones who cannibalized Breakdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.13,0:09:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And tried to gut me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.90,0:10:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M.E.C.H.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.28,0:10:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it would appear their knowledge of Cybertronian bio-tech has grown more sophisticated.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.52,0:10:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why would they want Bumblebee's part?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.65,0:10:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bumblebee, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.27,0:10:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are not presently equipped to handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.80,0:10:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are mistaken, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.94,0:10:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do know what it's like to lose a vital part of oneself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.79,0:10:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, as a result,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.07,0:10:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know the value of putting one's faith in the strength of those around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.96,0:10:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We vow to do everything in our power to make you whole again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.20,0:10:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if not, Ratchet can just make you a new...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.78,0:10:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,cog-thing. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.18,0:10:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.09,0:10:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miko! A T-cog is a bio-mechanism, not a scrap-yard find.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.96,0:10:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it were that easy don't you think
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.22,0:10:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would have replaced Bumblebee's voice-box by now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.12,0:11:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are not useless, Bee.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.68,0:11:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right all right,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.45,0:11:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I say none of us transform until Bumblebee gets his cog back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.35,0:11:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your spark’s in the right place, Bulkhead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.75,0:11:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't think now was the time to be limiting ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.63,0:11:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not with Megatron potentially seeking other Doomsday devices.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.36,0:11:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I fear not while MECH uses Bumblebee's T-cog
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.70,0:11:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for their own sinister purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.35,0:11:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commence beta-test.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.30,0:12:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Installation complete. Commencing scan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.62,0:12:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scan successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.82,0:12:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commencing transformation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.98,0:13:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the ones who turned poor Breakdown into a pitiful science experiment?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.10,0:13:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't learn much from the experience, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.26,0:13:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough to know where the soft spots are, Decepticon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.56,0:13:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh please. I am no longer affiliated with that entity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.14,0:13:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, if I were here to avenge the big lug,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.81,0:13:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you would be screaming for mercy by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.51,0:13:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.11,0:13:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To propose an alliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.17,0:13:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, we have much more in common than you might think.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.78,0:13:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I am not merely referring to our battle scars.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.08,0:13:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What could I possibly gain from such an arrangement?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.20,0:13:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Insider knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.87,0:14:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wise choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.02,0:14:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now. A T-cog isn't technology. It is biology.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.54,0:14:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means it will reject any power source other than energon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.26,0:14:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.28,0:14:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Energon is the fuel,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.50,0:14:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the ammunition and the lifeblood of all Cybertronians,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.07,0:14:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,whatever their affiliation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.39,0:14:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and I both want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.43,0:14:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And currently I lack the means of locating it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.93,0:14:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But once I supply you with the...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.07,0:14:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,particulars of its chemical make-up...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.68,0:14:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we can utilise your considerable resources
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.14,0:14:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to devise a means of detecting new deposits.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.36,0:14:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For us to share.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.46,0:15:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,IF the supply meets M.E.C.H.'s rather significant demand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.62,0:15:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aah... Intending to build an army, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.94,0:15:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am no stranger to ambition.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.37,0:15:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Optimus and Bulkhead haven't reported in yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.40,0:15:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bumblebee!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.62,0:15:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will let you know the moment I hear something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.61,0:15:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh for Primus' sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.61,0:15:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will someone keep him occupied so I can get some work done?!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.52,0:15:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Bee.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.79,0:15:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about a videogame?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.27,0:15:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bad call.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.44,0:15:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.16,0:15:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, no big deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.64,0:15:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That game is lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.18,0:15:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say we watch some TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.25,0:16:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The new Urbana 500. It won't just rock your world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.26,0:16:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will transform it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.92,0:16:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taking the "auto-" out of an Autobot is so not a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.94,0:16:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bee, c'mon! You're just as amazing without wheels!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.96,0:16:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, speed isn't everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.57,0:16:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Personal best, Arcee!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.98,0:16:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You hit 1:20 easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.09,0:16:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.90,0:16:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bumblebee! Where do you think you're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.67,0:16:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't just go for a walk!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.95,0:16:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are robots in disguise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.05,0:16:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leaving the base in this form puts you at risk of being seen
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.30,0:16:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and of us being discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.34,0:17:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You''ll just have to remain in the silo until...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.99,0:17:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... yes, Bumblebee. Until I can fix you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.46,0:17:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.57,0:17:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the lift home,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.49,0:17:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,friend of Jack's Mom who is a nurse at... at... the hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.03,0:17:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.62,0:17:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jack's at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.91,0:17:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miko's in detention... again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.10,0:17:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was expecting Bulkhead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.77,0:17:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I’m sorry to disappoint but he is on watch duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.48,0:17:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to ride with the siren on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.69,0:17:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.65,0:17:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This could be it. I'll alert the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.60,0:18:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you and I can handle it,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.82,0:18:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bee, but there is no reason to...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.56,0:18:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to prove?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.84,0:18:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ratchet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.31,0:18:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Bumblebee's voice-box?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.68,0:18:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was... severely damaged in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.36,0:18:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.47,0:18:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.88,0:18:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tragically, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.63,0:18:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It happened at Tyger-Pax.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.63,0:18:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.56,0:18:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our brave scout was captured by Megatron's forces and interrogated.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.51,0:18:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he refused to provide intel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.09,0:18:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And paid a grave price for his courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.17,0:18:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bumblebee was left for scrap.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.27,0:18:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Autobot troops found him and evacuated him to a triage facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.39,0:18:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where a field medic managed to stabilize his condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.32,0:18:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, we owe Bumblebee's life to that field medic?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.22,0:19:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's one way of looking at it, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.59,0:19:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though the medic... could have done better.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.43,0:19:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.29,0:19:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still don't know how you talked me into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.51,0:19:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're worse than Miko.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.14,0:19:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah-yeah-yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.37,0:19:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not every mission ends in a high-speed pursuit,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.97,0:19:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but without your...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.31,0:19:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. I'll drop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.39,0:19:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if Optimus finds out, this was not my idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.89,0:19:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Signal's coming from over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.46,0:19:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's coming our way, fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.15,0:19:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch me if you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.37,0:19:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.75,0:20:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. You get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.27,0:20:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sporting of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.58,0:20:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not even gotta try and shoot up my tires?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.01,0:20:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bumblebee! Where is your famous horse-power?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.48,0:20:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me some speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.43,0:20:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is with the rent-a-car?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.40,0:21:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd stick around and do some doughnuts around you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.79,0:21:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have a delivery to make.
